 Hellenistic letters, Alpha with straight bar, epsilon with short middle bar, zeta formed by vertical with horizontal bars top and bottom; Mu with four sloping strokes, full length; omicron, omega and theta all smaller than other letters; sigma with four equal strokes, top and bottom angled outwards; omega open with short horizontal tails. ",[40,49],{"type":41,"l":42,"from":43,"to":44,"h":45,"unit":46,"atLeast":47,"atMost":48},"letterHeight","Line 1-2","line1","line2","9-11","mm","9","11",{"type":50,"l":51,"from":43,"to":44,"unit":46},"interlinear","Interlineation line 1 to 2",{"_":53,"notBefore":54,"notAfter":55,"evidence":56},"4th century BCE",-400,-301,"lettering",[58,62],{"_":59,"type":60,"ref":61,"region":59},"Sicilia","ancient","http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462492",{"_":63,"type":64,"ref":65,"region":59},"Sicily","modern","http://sws.geonames.org/2523119",[],[],"Palermo",{"_":70,"role":71,"ref":72},"Museo Archeologico Regionale Antonino Salinas","museum","http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/museum/064",{"_":74,"type":75},"8796","inventory",{"_":77,"mainLang":78,"languages":79},"Ancient Greek","grc",[77],"491444",[82],{"atLeast":83,"atMost":84},9,11,[86,87,88,89,90,91,92,93,93,94,90,95,96],"Blackburne, 1749, Inscriptions in 1748 / 1749 collected by Thos Blackburne Esqr","Castelli, 1762, Le antiche iscrizioni di Palermo","Castelli, 1769, Siciliae et objacentium insularum veterum inscriptionum nova collectio","Castelli, 1784, Siciliae et objacentium insularum veterum inscriptionum nova collectio prolegomenis et notis illustrata, et iterum cum emendationibus, & auctariis evulgata","Boeckh, Franz, 1853, CIG","Kaibel, 1890, IG","Michel, 1897-1900, Recueil d’inscriptions grecques","Supplementum epigraphicum graecum, 1923-","Manni Piraino, 1973, IGMusPalermo","Manganaro, 1992, Massalioti per il Mediterraneo: tra Spagna, Sardegna e Sicilia","Gill, 1991, Greek Cult Tables",[98,99,100,101,102,103,104,105,105,106,102,107,108],"3MZMBB7L","4JP8QJ5H","SPTB56H3","7PSFHSUH","TQ